        "id": "2038799020152283243",
        "text": "Remember when the problem with EVs was the cost of the battery?\n\nYeah. Not a problem anymore. https://t.co/yC1RkiUPmz",
        "created_at": "Tue Mar 31 02:02:20 +0000 2026",
        "lang": "en",
        "media": [
          {
            "type": "photo",
            "id": "2038799012443115521",
